thread.title: BRIEF-Fidelity Southern Corporation Reports Q4 EPS of $0.46

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Fidelity Southern Corporation Reports Q4 EPS of $0.46
text:
Jan 18 (Reuters) - Fidelity Southern Corp:
* FIDELITY SOUTHERN CORPORATION REPORTS EARNINGS FOR FOURTH QUARTER OF $12.4 MILLION; $39.8 MILLION IN 2017
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.46 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.30 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* REVALUATION OF TAX CUTS & JOB ACT RESULTED ONE-TIME INCOME TAX BENEFIT OF ABOUT $4.9 MILLION, OR $0.18 OF DILUTED EPS, FOR Q4 OF 2017
* QTRLY NET INTEREST INCOME $35.9 MILLION VERSUS $32.9 MLN‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
